{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories","type":"ConceptScheme","title":{"en":"Project Categories","de":"Projektkategorien"},"description":{"en":"Project categories classify a project. At the first level, the categories denote the disciplines of art that describe (physical, digital, immaterial, conceptual) projects, works, and art objects. From the second level onward, the distinction to genres is not clearly defined.","de":"Projektkategorien typisieren ein Projekt. Die Kategorien bezeichnen in der ersten Ordnung die Gattungen der Kunst, die (materielle, digitale, immaterielle, konzeptuelle) Projekte/Werke/Kunstobjekte beschreiben. Ab der zweiten Ordnung ist der Übergang zu Genres nicht scharf trennbar."},"license":{"id":"https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/"},"hasTopConcept":[{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories#project-category-1","prefLabel":{"en":"Academic Publication","de":"Akademische Publikation"},"altLabel":{"en":["Scientific Publication","Research Publication"],"de":["Wissenschaftliche Publikation"]},"narrower":[{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories#project-category-2","prefLabel":{"en":"Doctoral Thesis","de":"Dissertation"},"altLabel":{"en":["Dissertation","PhD Thesis","Thesis"],"de":["Thesis"]}},{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories#project-category-3","prefLabel":{"en":"Podcast","de":"Podcast"}},{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories#project-category-4","prefLabel":{"en":"Website","de":"Webseite"}}]},{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project-categories#project-category-5","prefLabel":{"en":"Applied Arts","de":"Angewandte Kunst"},"altLabel":{"de":["Gestaltung","Kunstgewerbe"]},"narrower":[{"id":"https://docs.arkumu.nrw/documentation/controlled-vocabularies/project